Home> AboutA global force in pilot training, resourcing and simulationAboutL3 Airline Academy is part of L3 Commercial Training Solutions. We point with pride to a heritage that dates back to incredibly successful organizations within the commercial aviation arena – CTC Aviation, Aerosim Academy, Aerosim Technologies and L3 Link UK. Today, as L3 Commercial Training Solutions, we're at the global forefront of Airline Pilot training, resourcing and simulation.
 
Are you an aspiring Airline Pilot?
We offer various routes that lead to one of the most desirable careers on earth. We deliver training in purpose-built centers and in next-generation simulators and aircraft. Equally as important, we provide airline placement for our graduates with our Airline Partners.AboutLocationsFleet & ResourcesTraining FleetFlight SimulatorsComputer-Based TrainingApprovalsOur Parent CompanySafety & Compliance
